# Note (2026-04-28): benchmarks/results/**/*.jsonl and validation/*.jsonl
# are NOW COMMITTED for audit-trail-by-git-clone — reviewers run
# scripts/verify_headline.py --all against published JSONLs to
# reproduce per-model headline rates. Path B policy committed: v1
# raw + v1 PHR + v2 PHR + B4 trajectories. results_v2.jsonl is
# regenerable from results.jsonl + cotsuite.parsing in seconds via
# scripts/materialize_v2_normalized.py — not committed (saves ~38MB).
benchmarks/results/**/results_v2.jsonl
